<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.7">
<l>vēṟē kūṟuvatuṇ ṭaṭiyēṉvi ritturaikku</l>
<l>māṟē nīpaṇiyā taṭainiṉti rumaṉattu</l>
<l>kūṟēṉ neñcutaṉṉāl kuṇaṅkoṇṭumaṟ ṟōrteyvam</l>
<l>tēṟē ṉuṉṉaiyallāl tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is another thing that I, your devotee, am saying;</l>
<l>You secure [it] in your divine heart</l>
<l rend="indent">without demanding a means of [my] commenting elaborately.</l>
<l>I do not speak from [my] heart of another deity</l>
<l rend="indent">[even] considering [his] qualities;</l>
<l>I do not trust [any] but you, [Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
